## Panel Labeling

### Multi-Panel Figures

**Format**: (A), (B), (C), etc.

**Placement**: Top-left corner of each panel (in figure) or at start of description (in caption)

**Description order**: Left to right, top to bottom

**Example**:
```
Figure 5. [Title]. (A) [Panel A description]. (B) [Panel B description]. 
(C) [Panel C description]. (D) [Panel D description].
```

### Sub-Panels

**Format**: (A1), (A2), (B1), (B2), etc.

**Example**:
```
Figure 6. [Title]. (A) [Main panel A]. (A1) [Sub-panel A1]. (A2) [Sub-panel A2]. 
(B) [Main panel B]. (B1) [Sub-panel B1]. (B2) [Sub-panel B2].
```

